---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about">
	<div class="border-t border-stone-200 py-16 dark:border-stone-800 md:py-24">
		<p class="mb-8 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500">
			01. about
		</p>
		<div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400">
			<p>
				I'm a software engineer focused on Generative AI — specifically the architecture and backend
				work that makes AI systems scalable, secure, and production-ready.
			</p>
			<p>
				I bring years of backend development experience to the GenAI space. My work centres on the
				infrastructure, data pipelines, and tool-layer that surround the models: the part that
				transforms a demo into a product that actually ships.
			</p>
			<p>
				Outside of code, I value continuous learning — currently studying Chinese on top of keeping
				up my English. When I'm not at the keyboard I'm usually out on my motorbike, which turns out
				to be the best reset I've found.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Section>
